kaging or other issues, please provide feedback on our mailing list [2], IRC [3], and\/or file a bug against our PPA packages [4].<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>1. KDE bugtracker: https:\/\/bugs.kde.org<\/em><br><em>2. Kubuntu-devel mailing list: https:\/\/lists.ubuntu.com\/mailman\/listinfo\/kubuntu-devel<br>3. Kubuntu IRC channels: #kubuntu &amp; #kubuntu-devel on irc.freenode.net<br>4. Kubuntu ppa bugs: https:\/\/bugs.launchpad.net\/kubuntu-ppa<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We are pleased to announce that Plasma 5.17.1, is now available in our backports PPA for Kubuntu 19.10. The release announcement detailing the new features and improvements in Plasma 5.17 can be found here To upgrade: Add the following repository to your software sources list: ppa:kubuntu-ppa\/backports or if it is&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":20,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[129],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4265"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/20"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4265"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4265\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4267,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4265\/revisions\/4267"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4265"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4265"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4265"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"